_kaigo.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-介護関連業務</span></a>\n            <ul class=\"header__kaigo-list\">\n              <li><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_1.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-レンタルの仕組みについて</span></a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_2.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-レンタル商品</span></a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_3.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-販売商品</span></a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </li>\n          <li><a href=\"factory.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-工場案内</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"gyoumu_hote.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-その他業務</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"header__item js-header__item\">\n        <span class=\"header__link\">会社案内</span>\n        <ul class=\"dropdown-list\">\n          <li><a href=\"gaiyou_gai.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-会社情報</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"gaiyou_enkaku.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-沿革</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"gaiyou_net.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-当社ネットワーク</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"header__item js-header__item\">\n        <span class=\"header__link\"><a href=\"kyuzin.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>求人情報</span></a> </span>\n        <ul class=\"dropdown-list\">\n          <li><a href=\"kyuzin_1.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-新卒採用</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"kyuzin_toi.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-新卒採用Q&A</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"kyuzin_2.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-キャリア採用</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"kyuzin_3.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-スタッフ・パート採用</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"header__item js-header__item\">\n        <span class=\"header__link\"><a href=\"toi_all_1.html\" class=\"trans\">お問合わせ</a></span>\n        <ul class=\"dropdown-list list-right\">\n          <li><a href=\"toi_all_1.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-会社全体に対するお問合せ</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"toi_all_2.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-レンタル・商品に関するお問合せ</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"toi_all_3.html\" class=\"trans\"><span>-求人に対するお問合せ</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- SP メニュー -->\n  <ul class=\"header__list fb sp\">\n    <li class=\"header__item header__sp-heading header__top\"><a href=\"./\" class=\"trans\"><span class=\"header__link\">トップ</span></a></li>\n    <li class=\"header__item header__sp-border-b\">\n      <span class=\"header__link header__gyoumu\">業務案内</span>\n      <ul class=\"dropdown-list\">\n        <li class=\"header__sp-heading\"><a href=\"gyoumu_hos.html\" class=\"trans\">病院業務</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header__sp-heading\"><a href=\"gyoumu_mekin.html\" class=\"trans\">滅菌業務</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header__sp-heading dropdown\"><a href=\"#menu04\" class=\"secList header__sp-heading\"><span>介護関連業務</span></a></li>\n        <li class=\"header__sp-heading\"><a href=\"factory.html\" class=\"trans\">工場案内</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header__sp-heading\"><a href=\"gyoumu_hote.html\" class=\"trans\">その他業務</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"header__item dropdown\">\n      <a href=\"#menu01\" class='secList header__sp-heading'>会社案内</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"header__item dropdown\">\n      <a href=\"#menu02\" class='secList header__sp-heading'>求人情報</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"header__item dropdown\">\n      <a href=\"#menu03\" class='secList header__sp-heading'>お問合わせ</a>\n    </li>\n    <div id=\"menu01\" class=\"section\">\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gaiyou_gai.html\" class=\"trans\">会社情報</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gaiyou_enkaku.html\" class=\"trans\">沿革</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gaiyou_net.html\" class=\"trans\">当社ネットワーク</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"menu02\" class=\"section\">\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"kyuzin.html\" class=\"trans\">求人情報TOP</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"kyuzin_1.html\" class=\"trans\">新卒採用</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"kyuzin_toi.html\" class=\"trans\">新卒採用Q&A</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"kyuzin_2.html\" class=\"trans\">キャリア採用</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"kyuzin_3.html\" class=\"trans\">スタッフ・パート採用</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"menu03\" class=\"section\">\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"toi_all_1.html\" class=\"trans\">会社全体に対するお問合せ</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"toi_all_2.html\" class=\"trans\">レンタル・商品に関する<br>お問合せ</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"toi_all_3.html\" class=\"trans\">求人に対するお問合せ</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"menu04\" class=\"section\">\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo.html\" class=\"trans\">介護関連業務について</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_1.html\" class=\"trans\">レンタルの仕組みについて</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_2.html\" class=\"trans\">レンタル商品</a></p>\n      <p class=\"menu__item\"><a href=\"gyoumu_kaigo_3.html\" class=\"trans\">販売商品</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </ul>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"kyuzin\">\n  <section class=\"mv\">\n    <h2 class=\"mv__title\">新卒採用</h2>\n    <p><img src=\"images/kyuzin/mv01.jpg\" alt=\"新卒採用\"></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"contents inner\">\n    <section class=\"info\">\n      <p class=\"kyuzin__note\">面談/面接はwebでも実施しております。</p>\n      <h3 class=\"kyuzin__title\">求人情報－新卒採用　　<br class=\"sp\">令和９年４月採用は若干名</h3>\n      <table class=\"info__table\">\n        <tbody>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\">募集職種</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">職種</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">営業職</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\" rowspan=\"4\">待遇</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">初任給</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">\n              大卒　　　220,000円<br>\n              短大卒　　195,000円<br>\n              高卒　　　185,000円\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">初任給与支払日</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">毎月２５日（銀行振込）、給与計算締切日：毎月１５日</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">賞与</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">年２回（7月、１２月）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">昇給</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">年１回（毎年４月）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\" rowspan=\"4\">働く環境</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">勤務地</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">\n              【大卒・短大卒】<br>\n              富山本社・金沢支店・信越支店・新潟営業所・福井営業所・能登営業所<br>\n              【高卒】<br>\n              富山本社\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">勤務時間</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">\n              【富山本社・メディカル・金沢・信越・新潟・福井・能登】<br>\n              午前８時３０分～午後５時（実働７時間３０分／休憩1時間）<br>\n              【関東】<br>\n              午前９時００分～午後５時３０分（実働７時間３０分／休憩1時間）\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">休日</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">週休２日制　お盆・年末年始休暇　年間１１２日</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">休暇</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">年次有給休暇（１日、半日単位で休暇取得が可能）、特別休暇（慶弔休暇　等）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\">加入保険</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">社会保険</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">健康保険、厚生年金保険、雇用保険、労災保険へ加入</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\" rowspan=\"4\">福利厚生</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">退職金制度</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">あり</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">厚生施設</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">食堂（本社、信越工場、関東工場）</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">社内割引</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">社内割引価格で当社仕入商品を購入可能</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">その他制度</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">慶弔見舞金（結婚・出産お祝金　等）、業務外傷病時見舞金</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\">社内制度</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">各種制度</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">出産休暇、育児休業休暇、介護休暇、定年制／再雇用：６０歳定年／再雇用あり</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"info__tr\">\n            <th class=\"info__th01\">住まい</th>\n            <th class=\"info__th02\">借上社宅</th>\n            <td class=\"info__td\">\n              【大卒・短大卒】<br>\n              遠距離通勤となる場合は借上社宅制度適用　※家賃は会社負担85%（上限あり）\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"flow\">\n      <h3 class=\"kyuzin__title\">採用フロー</h3>\n      <ul class=\"flow__list fb\">\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">1</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">エントリー</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">2</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">会社説明会</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">3</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">書類選考<br>ＥＳ提出</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">4</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">人事面接<br>適性検査</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">5</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">役員面接</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">6</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">内定</p>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow__item\">\n          <p class=\"flow__num\">\n            <span class=\"flow__step\">STEP</span><br>\n            <span class=\"flow__n\">7</span>\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"flow__txt\">現場社員から<br class=\"pc\">業務説明</p>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"btns fb\">\n      <a href=\"kyuzin_toi.html\" class=\"trans btns__wrap MT0\"><p class=\"btns__btn btns--qa\">新卒採用 Ｑ＆Ａ</p></a>\n    </div>\n    \n    <section class=\"link\">\n      <ul class=\"link__list\">\n        <li class=\"link__item\">\n          <a href=\"kyuzin_2.html\" class=\"trans\">\n            <p class=\"link__txt\">キャリア採用</p>\n            <p class=\"link__more\">詳しくはこちら ＞</p>\n            <p class=\"link__img\"><img src=\"images/kyuzin/bg_link02.jpg\" alt=\"キャリア採用 詳しくはこちら ＞\"></p>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"link__item\">\n          <a href=\"kyuzin_3.html\" class=\"trans\">\n            <p class=\"link__txt\">スタッフ・パート採用</p>\n            <p class=\"link__more\">詳しくはこちら ＞</p>\n            <p class=\"link__img\"><img src=\"images/kyuzin/bg_link03.jpg\" alt=\"スタッフ・パート採用 詳しくはこちら ＞\"></p>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n  <ul class=\"footer__list fb\">\n    <li class=\"footer__item\">\n      <a href=\"gaiyou_gai.html\" class=\"trans\">\n        <p class=\"footer__bg\"><img src=\"images/common/